FT  05 FEB 92 / World News in Brief: Army pushes insurance
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The British army is to launch a campaign to persuade troops to take out life
insurance. Many found after the Gulf war began that they had insufficient
cover and were then unable to obtain it.
